title: Pure Storage FlashArray: Internal Alerts
agents: pure_storage_fa
catalog: hw/storagehw/pure_storage
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors open alerts from a Pure Storage FlashArray.

 The Checkmk state is {CRIT} if there are critical alerts, {WARN} if
 there are warning alerts and {OK} otherwise.

 To make this check work you have to configure the related special agent
 {Pure Storage FlashArray}.

discovery:
  One service is created.
